        <!-- Main Section -->
        <section class="my-5">
          <div class="container">
            <h2 class="text-primary mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
            <!-- FAQs Accordion -->
            <div class="accordion accordion-flush" id="accordionFlushExample">
              <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header">
                  <button
                    class="accordion-button collapsed"
                    type="button"
                    data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                    data-bs-target="#flush-collapseOne"
                    aria-expanded="false"
                    aria-controls="flush-collapseOne"
                  >
                    Brief me about Takshila Institute
                  </button>
                </h2>
                <div
                  id="flush-collapseOne"
                  class="accordion-collapse collapse"
                  data-bs-parent="#accordionFlushExample"
                >
                  <div class="accordion-body">
                    Takshila was founded in 1998 with a concept to provide objective centric
                    coaching education in a different innovative and affable learning environment in
                    satisfaction of students and to bring them in the frequency band of teacher so
                    that the scientific phenomenon of resonance become a reality. Takshila Institute
                    is committed to the vision to exemplify excellence and leadership in quality
                    education. We provide a platform where goals are achieved, skills are nurtured
                    and values are build.
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header">
                  <button
                    class="accordion-button collapsed"
                    type="button"
                    data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                    data-bs-target="#flush-collapseTwo"
                    aria-expanded="false"
                    aria-controls="flush-collapseTwo"
                  >
                    Where is Takshila Institute located?
                  </button>
                </h2>
                <div
                  id="flush-collapseTwo"
                  class="accordion-collapse collapse"
                  data-bs-parent="#accordionFlushExample"
                >
                  <div class="accordion-body">
                    Our corporate office is located on Delhi - D-11/148, Sec-8, (Opp. Metro Pillar
                    No. 390), Rohini, New Delhi. However, we have 15 more centres in Delhi NCR and
                    other parts of India. Details in our website in Contact Us.
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header">
                  <button
                    class="accordion-button collapsed"
                    type="button"
                    data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                    data-bs-target="#flush-collapseThree"
                    aria-expanded="false"
                    aria-controls="flush-collapseThree"
                  >
                    Do we need to submit the original certificates on the day of admission?
                  </button>
                </h2>
                <div
                  id="flush-collapseThree"
                  class="accordion-collapse collapse"
                  data-bs-parent="#accordionFlushExample"
                >
                  <div class="accordion-body">
                    No. there is no need to submit original certificates but candidate must produce
                    original certificates/documents on the day of admission for their verifications,
                    failing which candidate shall not be considered for admission. Two sets of
                    self-attested copies of the certificates/documents are required to be submitted
                    at the time of physical counselling as detailed in the admission brochure. The
                    same should be collected back by the student soon after physical counselling.
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header">
                  <button
                    class="accordion-button collapsed"
                    type="button"
                    data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                    data-bs-target="#flush-collapseFour"
                    aria-expanded="false"
                    aria-controls="flush-collapseFour"
                  >
                    Brief me about Takshila Institute
                  </button>
                </h2>
                <div
                  id="flush-collapseFour"
                  class="accordion-collapse collapse"
                  data-bs-parent="#accordionFlushExample"
                >
                  <div class="accordion-body">
                    Takshila was founded in 1998 with a concept to provide objective-centric
                    coaching education in a different innovative and affable learning environment.
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header">
                  <button
                    class="accordion-button collapsed"
                    type="button"
                    data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                    data-bs-target="#flush-collapseFive"
                    aria-expanded="false"
                    aria-controls="flush-collapseFive"
                  >
                    Who should join the Foundation Course?
                  </button>
                </h2>
                <div
                  id="flush-collapseFive"
                  class="accordion-collapse collapse"
                  data-bs-parent="#accordionFlushExample"
                >
                  <div class="accordion-body">
                    Students studying in classes VIII to X who aspire to excel in their board exams
                    and build a strong foundation for competitive exams should consider this course.
                    It is ideal for students seeking conceptual clarity and personal growth.
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header">
                  <button
                    class="accordion-button collapsed"
                    type="button"
                    data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                    data-bs-target="#flush-collapseSix"
                    aria-expanded="false"
                    aria-controls="flush-collapseSix"
                  >
                    How does the Foundation Course differ from private tuitions?
                  </button>
                </h2>
                <div
                  id="flush-collapseSix"
                  class="accordion-collapse collapse"
                  data-bs-parent="#accordionFlushExample"
                >
                  <div class="accordion-body">
                    The Foundation Course offers comprehensive study material, detailed syllabus
                    coverage, competitive assignments, and resources like libraries equipped with
                    competitive books. It also provides a structured learning environment that
                    fosters critical thinking, unlike private tuitions, which may focus solely on
                    solving specific queries.
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header">
                  <button
                    class="accordion-button collapsed"
                    type="button"
                    data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                    data-bs-target="#flush-collapseSeven"
                    aria-expanded="false"
                    aria-controls="flush-collapseSeven"
                  >
                    What additional benefits will students get in the Foundation Course?
                  </button>
                </h2>
                <div
                  id="flush-collapseSeven"
                  class="accordion-collapse collapse"
                  data-bs-parent="#accordionFlushExample"
                >
                  <div class="accordion-body">
                    Students gain problem-solving skills, analytical thinking, and exam
                    preparedness. They are guided to strengthen key concepts of Science and
                    Mathematics, ensuring readiness for exams like IIT-JEE, NEET, and other
                    competitive entrances. The course also includes motivational sessions and
                    resources for overall development.
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header">
                  <button
                    class="accordion-button collapsed"
                    type="button"
                    data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                    data-bs-target="#flush-collapseEight"
                    aria-expanded="false"
                    aria-controls="flush-collapseEight"
                  >
                    Are sufficient reference books available in the library?
                  </button>
                </h2>
                <div
                  id="flush-collapseEight"
                  class="accordion-collapse collapse"
                  data-bs-parent="#accordionFlushExample"
                >
                  <div class="accordion-body">
                    Yes, the institute provides an updated collection of reference books and study
                    modules that meet the students' academic needs.
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
